sections.Behind the scenes:
*The hand that Davos loses fingers from has been changed from his left to his right, a result of actor Liam Cunningham being left-handed.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.accesshollywood.com/access-countdown-to-game-of-thrones-season-2-qanda-liam-cunningham-talks-davos-seaworth_article_59908 Access Hollywood interview]&lt;/ref&gt;
*While some CGI was used to show the illusion of Davos not having fingertips, most of the time Liam Cunningham just wore a glove and kept his fingers bent inside. While effective and cheap, this did cause him some pain when it came to straightening his fingers out once shooting was finished for the day.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.sfx.co.uk/2012/03/27/game-of-thrones-season-two-liam-cunningham-interview/ SFX Magazine interview]&lt;/ref&gt;
*It has been confirmed that he is one of the favorite characters of producer and showrunner [[David Benioff]].
*On the [[Season 2]] Blu-ray, Davos narrates a [[Histories &amp; Lore]] video on '''&quot;[[Robert's Rebellion (Histories &amp; Lore)|Robert's Rebellion]]&quot;'''.

